Package: rfgfs
Type: Package
Title: Flight planner and companion package for FlightGear
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2016-05-08
Author: Theodore Lytras
Maintainer: Theodore Lytras <thlytras@gmail.com>
Depends:
    sp
Description: Automatically plans a route between two airports, using the
    airway and navaid data that ship with FlightGear, and writes this flight plan 
    to a csv or kml file (that can be opened with Google Earth).
    Also includes functions to communicate with FlightGear, calculate magnetic 
    declination using the same formula that FlightGear (via SimGear) uses, and 
    various others. FOR FLIGHT SIMULATION USE ONLY - NOT FOR REAL WORLD NAVIGATION.
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
